{"id":232925445,"title":"金門獅山砲陣地","content":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/3b062cf2-5097-4131-8b49-7672886b42fd/1280.jpeg\n獅山砲陣地位在山后民俗文化村後面的獅山，是現存唯一的坑道式榴彈砲陣地，又名為震東坑道，取「威震金東」的意涵。\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/50e11df0-5cfa-43b9-b9b0-7663f06c1780/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/937d44c9-b3ae-42f7-b2ff-d05d4216b1d9/1280.jpeg\n獅山砲陣地裡保留了許多往年戰役使用過的砲台及砲彈，其中美國製造的八吋榴砲，在「八二三」砲戰後期揚威戰場，發揮扭轉戰局的戰功。\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/aa54d5a5-9724-43a9-9e37-09776e831bb6/1280.jpeg\n獅山砲陣地一天有6場的8吋榴彈砲砲操\n砲操表演時間：\n每日上午二場（10：00、11：00）、下午四場（13：30、14：30、15：30、16：30）共六場\n\nhttps://www.dcard.tw/v2/vivid/videos/eaa997db-2c8f-4f76-bed4-f970627bd5e4?r=0.5625","excerpt":"獅山砲陣地位在山后民俗文化村後面的獅山，是現存唯一的坑道式榴彈砲陣地，又名為震東坑道，取「威震金東」的意涵。獅山砲陣地裡保留了許多往年戰役使用過的砲台及砲彈，其中美國製造的八吋榴砲，在「八二三」砲戰後","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"a255fb97-4199-4bd0-9b28-1ec2c0d2f382","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-20T09:47:23.012Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-20T09:47:23.012Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["金門景點","金門旅遊","遊記"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"旅遊","forumAlias":"travel","school":"國立臺中科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":true,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/3b062cf2-5097-4131-8b49-7672886b42fd/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/50e11df0-5cfa-43b9-b9b0-7663f06c1780/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/937d44c9-b3ae-42f7-b2ff-d05d4216b1d9/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/aa54d5a5-9724-43a9-9e37-09776e831bb6/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://vivid.dcard.tw/Public/eaa997db-2c8f-4f76-bed4-f970627bd5e4/thumbnail.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","m